definitions.definition: A kind of aggregate fruit in which the ovaries cohere in a solid mass, with a slender receptacle, as in the magnolia .
A similar multiple fruit, such as a mulberry .

main_definition: ( botany ) A kind of aggregate fruit in which the ovaries cohere in a solid mass, with a slender receptacle, as in the magnolia .
secondary_definitions: ( botany ) A similar multiple fruit, such as a mulberry .
